          <strong>Beta status.</strong> Some or all features of the Service are currently in beta. Beta features are provided "AS IS" for evaluation, may have bugs, may be modified or discontinued, and are not subject to the warranties or service-level commitments that may apply to generally available offerings.
        </p>
        <p class="mt-3">
          <strong>What we do not commit to.</strong> Unless explicitly stated in a separate written agreement, we do not commit to:
        </p>
        <ul class="mt-3 list-disc pl-6 space-y-1">
